OL,4,G2100FArt of Scandinavia
OL,5,     GAndrew Graham-Dixon explores the
OL,6,     Gextraordinary art to come out of
OL,7,     Gthe dark Norwegian soul, most
OL,8,     Gfamous for producing The Scream
OL,9,     Gby Edvard Munch.
OL,10,G2200FThe Sky at Night
OL,11,     GThe team explore the remarkable
OL,12,     Gstory of Jodrell Bank Observatory
OL,13,     Gand its towering Lovell
OL,14,     GTelescope, which scientists have
OL,15,     Gused to listen to the cosmos for
OL,16,     Galmost 70 years.
